fields.name: 3/2mm Synergy - Chest Zip Wetsuit for Women
ROXY WOMENS 4/3MM POP SURF CHEST ZIP WETSUIT
fields.description: POP Surf is about sustainable style that performs. This ultra-light and stretchy chest zip wetsuit blends pop printed panelling with the cutting-edge innovation of our StretchFlight x3 limestone neoprene and WarmFlight thermal fleece lining for a form-flattering silhouette that offers warmth and insulation.
